ore%20likely%20to%20use%20AI%20at%20work%20than%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20worker%20has%20habits%20and%20traits%20that%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20workplace%20from%20the%20overachievers%20to%20the%20social%20butterflies%2C%20and%20a%20new%20report%20by%20Slack%20has%20categorized%20them%20all%20into%20five%20workplace%20personalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslack.com%2Fintl%2Fen-gb%2Fblog%2Fproductivity%2F2023-office-personas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESlack%20published%20a%20new%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20%26quot%3Bworkplace%20personas%26quot%3B%20that%20surveyed%2015%2C492%20employed%20adults%20across%20nine%20countries%20including%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Australia%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20through%20a%20qualitative%20online%20survey%20between%20September%20and%20October%202023.%C2%A0The%20survey%20was%20undertaken%20by%20polling%20firm%20YouGov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20found%20that%20there%20are%20five%20common%20personalities%20you're%20likely%20to%20enter%20at%20work%2C%20giving%20each%20one%20a%20nickname%3A%20the%20detectives%2C%20the%20road%20warriors%2C%20the%20problem%20solvers%2C%20the%20networkers%2C%20and%20the%20expressionists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFind%20out%20which%20workplace%20persona%20you%20and%20your%20colleagues%20fit%20into%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Detective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2030%25%20of%20workers%20are%20detectives%2C%20Slack%20says%2C%20and%20they're%20known%20for%20always%20being%20on%20top%20of%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Binnate%20drive%20towards%20searching%20for%20and%20finding%20solutions%2C%20answers%2C%20information%2C%20and%20sharing%20with%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20report.%20Their%20standout%20traits%20include%20being%20curious%2C%20outcomes-driven%2C%20self-starters%2C%20and%20reliably%20in%20the%20know.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20half%20of%20detectives%20are%20driven%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%20and%20job%20security%20with%2093%25%20describing%20themselves%20as%20organized%20and%2091%25%20saying%20they%20like%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20their%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20colleagues%20tend%20to%20agree.%20Over%20half%20of%20colleagues%20say%20they%20are%20best%20at%20knowing%20everything%20that's%20going%20on%20at%20the%20company%20and%2038%25%20say%20they're%20good%20at%20digging%20up%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Road%20Warrior%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoad%20warriors%20tend%20to%20like%20to%20do%20things%20on%20their%20own%20terms%2C%20with%2022%25%20fitting%20into%20this%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20probably%20working%20remotely%20and%20from%20different%20locations%20at%20different%20times%20and%20are%20good%20at%20building%20connections%20virtually.%20They're%20outgoing%2C%20affable%2C%20and%20keen%20to%20use%20new%20workplace%20tools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20two-thirds%20describe%20themselves%20as%20flexible%20with%20just%20over%20half%20saying%20they%20like%20to%20work%20in%20a%20way%20that%20suits%20their%20schedule.%2089%25%20work%20away%20from%20their%20desks%20and%2081%25%20say%20they're%20adaptable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20colleagues%20say%20they're%20best%20at%20networking%20virtually%20and%20from%20anywhere%2C%20and%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20working%20from%20a%20new%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Networker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20identify%20networkers%20because%20they're%20always%20talking%20to%20someone%20and%20have%20connections%20on%20every%20team.%20They%20make%20up%2022%25%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20love%20socializing%20and%20collaborating%20with%20people%20and%20are%20probably%20in%20the%20office%20most%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetworkers%20largely%20describe%20themselves%20as%20extroverted%20and%20agree%20that%20you%20can%20be%20friends%20with%20your%20colleagues.%20Over%20half%20feel%20it's%20important%20to%20keep%20everyone%20updated%20and%2030%25%20like%20to%20foster%20connections%20with%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20peers%20say%20they're%20good%20at%20connecting%20everyone%20with%20the%20information%20they%20need%20and%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20have%20friends%20across%20teams%20and%20business%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Problem%20Solver%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20describe%20themselves%20as%20problem%20solvers%20are%20all%20about%20efficiency%20and%20make%20up%2016%25%20of%20workers%20in%20Slack's%20report.%20They're%20obsessed%20with%20saving%20time%2C%20being%20more%20productive%2C%20and%20having%20a%20hack%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E25%25%20like%20to%20share%20time-saving%20hacks%20and%20automation%20with%20their%20team%20and%20over%20half%20like%20to%20save%20time%20by%20getting%20rid%20of%20mundane%20and%20repetitive%20tasks.%2092%25%20describe%20themselves%20as%20early%20tech%20adopters%20and%2077%25%20say%20they're%20excited%20about%20using%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E37%25%20of%20problem%20solvers%20are%20already%20using%20AI%20at%20work%2C%20more%20than%20every%20other%20personality%20except%20the%20expressionist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20colleagues%20say%20they're%20good%20at%20streamlining%20tasks%20and%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20use%20new%20technologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Expressionist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20fun-loving%20and%20joyful%20colleague%20is%20probably%20an%20expressionist%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20Only%2010%25%20of%20workers%20fit%20into%20this%20persona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpressionists%20are%20visual%20and%20don't%20take%20themselves%20too%20seriously.%20They%20love%20to%20express%20themselves%20informally%20with%20memes%2C%20emojis%2C%20and%20gifs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E72%25%20of%20expressionists%20like%20using%20emojis%20and%20gifs%20to%20communicate%20in%20ways%20their%20colleagues%20will%20better%20understand%2C%20appreciate%2C%20and%20enjoy.%20Almost%20half%20feel%20workplace%20communication%20should%20be%20fun%20and%20lighthearted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20road%20warrior%2C%20colleagues%20think%20expressionists%20are%20great%20at%20connecting%20with%20people%20virtually%20while%20working%20from%20anywhere.%20They%20also%20think%20expressionists%20use%20the%20most%20fun%20emojis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20the%20problem%20solvers%2C%20around%2044%25%20of%20this%20workplace%20personality%20are%20already%20using%20AI%20at%20work%20or%20trying%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20incorporate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-the-five-different-personalities-in-the-workplace-report-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699452872000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65450e783cc84b4dfafbd8dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-the-five-different-personalities-in-the-workplace-report-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Slack%20published%20a%20new%20report%20today%20that%20surveyed%2015%2C492%20employed%20adults%20across%20nine%20locations%20including%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-the-five-different-personalities-in-the-workplace-report-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mortgage%20rates%20log%20biggest%20drop%20in%20over%20a%20year%20amid%20falling%20bond%20yields%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Home%20for%20sale%20sign%20housing%20market%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654b9170b788914e55524ccf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%