rban%20War%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20have%20encircled%20Gaza%20City%20and%20what%20exists%20now%20is%20north%20and%20south%20Gaza%20after%20striking%20the%20important%20Salah-Al-Din%20road%20that%20runs%20north-south.%20The%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmud%20Abbas%20has%20denounced%20Israel's%20offensive%20as%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20IDF%20calls%20it%20its%20mission%20to%20uproot%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20full%20ground%20invasion%2C%20Israel%20conducted%20relentless%20air%20strikes%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20structures%20and%20hit%20the%20'Gaza%20Metro'%2C%20a%20secret%20web%20of%20tunnels%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFighting%20in%20Built-up%20Areas%20(FIBUA)%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20an%20area%20dense%20with%20buildings%20and%20structures%20will%20entail%20lethal%20urban%20warfare%2C%20posing%20severe%20challenges%20for%20the%20Israeli%20ground%20troops%20and%20armoured%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20lanes%20of%20Gaza%20may%20not%20be%20the%20ideal%20place%20for%20armoured%20units%20like%20tanks%20or%20Infantry%20Fighting%20Vehicles%20(IFVs)%20to%20move%20as%20Hams%20operatives%20may%20use%20buildings%20to%20fire%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles.%20Hamas%20has%20claimed%20that%20intense%20fighting%20broke%20out%20when%20Israel%20entered%20Gaza%20and%20fired%20machine%20guns%20and%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%20(ATGMs)%20at%20the%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20targeted%20the%20observation%20posts%20and%20anti-tank%20missile%20launch%20posts%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20showed%20how%20vulnerable%20tanks%20and%20troops%20can%20be%20to%20ATGMs%20when%20not%20supported%20by%20Close%20Air%20Support%20(CAS).%20Russian%20tanks%20were%20sitting%20ducks%20for%20Molotov%20Cocktails%20thrown%20from%20buildings%20and%20built-up%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20Molotov%20Cocktails%2C%20even%20Kamikaze%20drones%20targeted%20Russian%20T-72%2C%20exposing%20the%20design%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20'Jack-In-The-Box'%20design%20of%20the%20tanks.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20operates%20Russian%20T-72%20and%20T-90%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELearning%20from%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20Israel%20is%20now%20installing%20metal%20roofs%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bcope-cages%26quot%3B%2C%20on%20tanks%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20munitions%20and%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Cope%20Cages%20on%20top%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Cope%20Cages%20on%20top%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F0f7kh32g_israeli-tanks-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E'Cope%20Cage'%20on%20top%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20Just%20tanks%20but%20even%20ground%20troops%20are%20exposed%20to%20surprise%20attacks%20from%20hideouts%20and%20ambushes%20from%20the%20'Gaza%20Metro'%2C%20a%20web%20of%20secret%20tunnels%20built%20by%20Hamas%20to%20supply%2C%20store%20weapons%2C%20hit%20and%20run%20after%20guerilla%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20developed%20a%20new%20weapon%20called%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-are-israels-new-secret-weapon-sponge-bombs-and-how-they-work-4522254%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3BSponge%20Bombs%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20neutralise%20the%20tunnel%20threat%20but%20the%20IDF%20intelligence%20says%20that%20Hamas%20has%20kept%20the%20hostages%20in%20these%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20Operation%20Pawan%2C%20the%20Indian%20Peacekeeping%20Forces%20(IPKF)%20faced%20the%20challenges%20of%20FIBUA%20when%20the%20LTTE%20operatives%20carried%20out%20guerilla%20attacks%20and%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Devices%20(IED)%20attacks%20on%20roads%20and%20junctions%20leading%20to%20Jaffna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWell-entrenched%20LTTE%20cadres%20attacked%20the%20IPKF%20from%20unknown%20positions%2C%20and%20poor%20ground%20intelligence%20of%20the%20area%20resulted%20in%20heavy%20casualties%20to%20the%20Brigade%20comprising%20of%20the%204%2F5%20Gorkhas%2C%205%20Para%20and%204%20Mahar%20suffered%20over%20200%20casualties%20until%206%20Guards%2C%20the%20Striking%20Sixth%20was%20assigned%20the%20task%20to%20break%20through%20and%20reach%20Jaffna%20Fort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelta%20Company%20under%20Capt%20Anil%20Chatta%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20commanding%20officer%20Col%20B%20R%20Bhatia%2C%20Shaurya%20Chakra%20(SC)%2C%20broke%20through%20the%20cordon%20using%20an%20innovative%20approach%20of%20going%20cross-country%20in%20pitch%20darkness%20using%20maps%20from%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20street%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%20is%20expected%20to%20stretch%20for%20weeks%20and%20Israel%20has%20to%20maintain%20supply%20lines%20when%20fighting%20deep%20in%20hostile%20territory%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20probability%20of%20ambushes%20is%20very%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armyupress.army.mil%2FJournals%2FMilitary-Review%2FEnglish-Edition-Archives%2FJan-Feb-2019%2FArnold-Mosul%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20liberation%20of%20Mosul%20by%20US-led%20forces%20from%20ISIS%20in%20Ira%3C%2Fa%3Eq%20serves%20as%20a%20lesson%20for%20operations%20in%20a%20Dense%20Urban%20Environment%20(DUE).%20Large-scale%20combat%20operations%20are%20required%20to%20capture%20a%20modern%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsolating%20a%20city%20is%20impossible%20when%20the%20lines%20between%20a%20combatant%20and%20a%20civilian%20are%20blurred%20and%20the%20depth%20and%20duration%20increase%20the%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20Israeli%20troops%20would%20be%20required%20to%20completely%20capture%20Gaza%2C%20which%20can%20result%20in%20high%20civilian%20and%20troop%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourth%20-%20The%20Battle%20Of%20Perception%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20global%20concerns%20over%20a%20major%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20has%20continued%20its%20operation.%20The%20next%20big%20challenge%20for%20Israel%20would%20be%20the%20Battle%20of%20Perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%209%2C700%20people%20have%20died%20and%20the%20UN%20has%20warned%20that%20a%20ground%20invasion%20may%20significantly%20increase%20civilian%20casualty%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%202017%20report%20by%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icrc.org%2Fen%2Fpublication%2Fi-saw-my-city-die-voices-front-lines-urban-conflict-iraq-syria-and-yemen%5C%22%3E'I%20Saw%20My%20City%20Die%3C%2Fa%3E'%2C%20highlights%20how%20deadly%20Urban%20warfare%20is%20to%20civilians%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20the%20war%20in%20cities%20caused%20eight%20times%20more%20casualties%20than%20fighting%20in%20other%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20has%20a%20population%20density%20of%205%2C500%20people%20per%20sq%20km%20and%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20innocent%20may%20not%20end%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699450500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fmt37vc5g_israeli-troops-in-gaza-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-cut-into-2-key-challenges-for-israel-in-gazas-urban-war-explained-4557765%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel-Gaza%20War%3A%20The%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20have%20encircled%20Gaza%20City%20and%20what%20exists%20now%20is%20north%20and%20south%20Gaza%20after%20striking%20the%20important%20Salah-Al-Din%20road%20that%20runs%20north-south.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-cut-into-2