%20duties%20in%20hostile%20terrains%20and%20safeguard%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20borders%20alongside%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Despite%20their%20significant%20contributions%2C%20they%20have%20been%20clubbed%20with%20civilian%20counterparts%20under%20the%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS)%2C%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cdiscriminatory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20this%20discrimination%20to%20end%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20have%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fex-paramilitary-body-seeks-meeting-with-pm-modi-over-demand-to-restore-old-pension-scheme%2Fcid%2F1978385%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20personnel%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%2C%20have%20long%20felt%20neglected%20and%20discriminated%20against%20in%20comparison%20to%20their%20counterparts%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20introduce%20the%20NPS%20in%202004%20replaced%20the%20regular%20pension%20scheme%20for%20paramilitary%20jawans%2C%20placing%20them%20in%20a%20contributory%20system%20that%20many%20argue%20is%20unfair%20and%20inadequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECore%20demands%3A%20Pension%20restoration%20and%20pay%20parity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20demand%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20Confederation%20is%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20OPS%20for%20paramilitary%20personnel%2C%20a%20benefit%20currently%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20army%2C%20navy%2C%20and%20air%20force.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20association%20is%20pressing%20for%20salaries%20equivalent%20to%20those%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20for%20serving%20paramilitary%20personnel.%20This%20would%20address%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20pay%20scales%2C%20where%20paramilitary%20personnel%20receive%20significantly%20lower%20salaries%20for%20their%20risk-prone%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famrit-kaal-and-the-two-types-of-retired-old-men%5C%22%3EAmrit%20Kaal%20and%20the%20Two%20Types%20of%20Retired%20Old%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20association%20is%20seeking%20an%20exemption%20from%20goods%20and%20services%20tax%20(GST)%20at%20central%20police%20canteens%2C%20aligning%20it%20with%20the%20privileges%20offered%20to%20the%20defense%20forces.%20These%20demands%20underscore%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20bridge%20the%20existing%20gaps%20and%20treat%20paramilitary%20personnel%20with%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20and%20frustration%3A%20The%20battle%20for%20recognition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20veterans%20have%20been%20vocal%20about%20their%20grievances%2C%20staging%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20plight.%20Their%20past%20protests%2C%20including%20one%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famrit-kaal-and-the-two-types-of-retired-old-men%5C%22%3ESeptember%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20highlighted%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20policy%20reforms%20and%20fair%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParamilitary%20veterans%20have%20highlighted%20the%20discriminatory%20practices%20that%20have%20persisted%20for%20years.%20They%20have%20been%20part%20of%20crucial%20battles%2C%20including%20the%201965%2C%201971%2C%20and%201999%20Kargil%20wars%2C%20standing%20alongside%20the%20army%20as%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence.%20Despite%20their%20sacrifices%20and%20contributions%2C%20they%20say%2C%20their%20pension%20benefits%20have%20been%20curtailed%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20discontent%20and%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fparamilitary-forces-armed-forces-of-union-old-pension-scheme-applicable-to-personnel-of-all-capfs-delhi-high-court-218774%5C%22%3Eruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20in%20January%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20paramilitary%20forces%20were%20deemed%20as%20%E2%80%98Armed%20Forces%20of%20the%20Union%2C%E2%80%99%20making%20them%20eligible%20for%20pensions%20under%20OPS.%20The%20court%20directed%20the%20government%20to%20implement%20this%20decision%20within%20three%20weeks.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20chose%20to%20challenge%20the%20ruling%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20appeal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20resolution%20of%20this%20crucial%20matter%20has%20been%20deferred%20until%202024%2C%20raising%20concerns%20and%20questions%20about%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Confederation%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20signifies%20a%20tipping%20point%20in%20the%20struggle%20for%20recognition%20and%20equality.%20The%20veterans%2C%20along%20with%20the%20serving%20paramilitary%20personnel%2C%20are%20determined%20to%20make%20their%20voices%20heard%2C%20highlighting%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20policy%20reforms%20that%20address%20their%20concerns%20comprehensively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699450228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27135014%2FScreenshot-2023-09-27-at-1.36.28-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fparamilitary-veterans-demand-restoration-of-old-pension-scheme-knock-at-pm-modis-door%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government's%20move%20to%20introduce%20the%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20in%202004%2C%20replacing%20the%20regular%20pension%20scheme%20and%20placing%20them%20in%20a%20contributory%20system%2C%20has%20been%20unfair%20to%20paramilitary%20jawans%2C%20they%20allege.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fparamilitary-veterans-demand-restoration-of-old-pension-schem