0removed%20by%20a%20surgeon%20so%20a%20large%20robot%20can%20insert%20a%20series%20of%20electrodes%20and%20superthin%20wires%20into%20their%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKingsman%3A%20The%20Secret%20Service%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20stars%20Colin%20Firth%2C%20Samuel%20L.%20Jackson%2C%20and%20Taron%20Egerton%2C%20features%20a%20similar%20neural%20implant%20as%20a%20key%20plot%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20movie%20%E2%80%94%20which%20parodies%20British%20spy%20films%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BJames%20Bond%26quot%3B%20series%20%E2%80%94%20eccentric%20tech%20tycoon%20Richmond%20Valentine%2C%20played%20by%20Jackson%2C%20announces%20a%20plan%20to%20give%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%20SIM%20cards%20with%20free%20phone%20and%20internet%20access.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catch%3F%20The%20SIM%20has%20to%20be%20implanted%20in%20your%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20climate%20change%20scientist%20is%20killed%20when%20his%20chip%20%E2%80%94%20implanted%20behind%20his%20ear%20like%20Neuralink%20%E2%80%94%20explodes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20movie%20progresses%2C%20it%20transpires%20that%20Jackson's%20character%20can%20control%20the%20chips%20remotely%2C%20and%20wants%20to%20put%20into%20motion%20a%20Malthusian%20plan%20to%20cut%20the%20increasing%20global%20population%20by%20triggering%20a%20signal%20from%20the%20chips%20that%20makes%20their%20users%20kill%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20chips%20have%20been%20implanted%20in%20the%20brains%20of%20the%20global%20elite%2C%20from%20wealthy%20executives%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20secret%20service%2C%20with%20the%20elites%20signing%20up%20to%20Valentine's%20plan%20in%20exchange%20for%20protection%20from%20his%20deadly%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20plan%20is%20scuppered%20as%20the%20secret%20agent%20Eggsy%2C%20played%20by%20Egerton%20%E2%80%94%20a%20member%20of%20the%20organization%20%26quot%3BKingsman%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20sneaks%20into%20Valentine's%20bunker%2C%20while%20another%20agent%20hacks%20into%20the%20implants%20and%20makes%20them%20explode%2C%20killing%20the%20elite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20film%2C%20which%20grossed%20over%20%24400%20million%20worldwide%2C%20came%20out%20two%20years%20before%20Neuralink%20was%20founded%20%E2%80%94%20though%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20Musk%20took%20any%20inspiration%20from%20a%20mid-budget%20action%20movie%20for%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20unlikely%20Musk%20will%20look%20to%20ape%20Jackson's%20fictional%20Valentine%20by%20controlling%20people's%20minds%20with%20Neuralink's%20chips%2C%20or%20cutting%20the%20world's%20population.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-wrong-about-fertility-rates-global-warming-demographers-say-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20is%20certainly%20not%20a%20believer%20in%20depopulation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20frequently%20stated%20his%20belief%20that%20the%20planet%20needs%20more%20people%20on%20it%2C%20not%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuralink%20is%20also%20evidently%20wary%20of%20any%20potential%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShivon%20Zilis%2C%20Neuralink's%20director%20of%20special%20projects%20and%20mother%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-shivon-zilis-children-twins-ivf-population-sperm-donor-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwins%20with%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20joked%20with%20Vance%20%E2%80%94%20referring%20to%20a%20number%20of%20failed%20rocket%20launches%20for%20SpaceX%2C%20another%20of%20Musk's%20companies%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20blow%20up%20the%20first%20three.%20That's%20not%20an%20option%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musks-wildly-popular-neuralink-is-eerily-similar-to-spy-movie-kingsman-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699449968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22