han%20a%20third%20-%2034%20per%20cent%20-%20of%20families%20in%20Bihar%20live%20in%20poverty%2C%20surviving%20on%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month%20or%20less%2C%20according%20to%20a%20detailed%20report%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20tabled%20in%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20yesterday.%20Forty-two%20per%20cent%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20households%20are%20among%20the%20poorest.%20This%20socio-economic%20data%20is%20even%20more%20appalling%20in%20a%20caste-driven%20Bihar%20where%20politics%20has%20revolved%20around%20Dalit%20and%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20votes%20after%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20reflects%20considerable%20poverty%20among%20the%20upper%20castes%20-%20more%20than%2025%20per%20cent.%20The%20poverty%20ratio%20was%20surprisingly%20high%20for%20the%20Bhumihars%20(27.58%20per%20cent)%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20land-owning%20caste%20of%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20Bihar%20was%20the%20poorest%20and%20most%20backward%20with%20the%20lowest%20literacy%20rate%20in%20the%20country%3B%20in%202023%2C%20it%20remains%20the%20same.%20In%20this%20year's%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20on%20the%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%2C%20Bihar%20stayed%20on%20top%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20proportion%20of%20multi-dimensionally%20poor%20people%26quot%3B.%20Along%20with%20the%20lowest%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20Bihar%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20performer%20in%20maternal%20and%20child%20health%2C%20housing%2C%20water%20and%20sanitation%2C%20school%20attendance%2C%20electricity%2C%20assets%20and%20numerous%20other%20human%20development%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistorical%20legacies%20like%20the%20zamindari%20system%20and%20fiscal%20equalisation%2C%20have%20influenced%20Bihar's%20economic%20landscape%20and%20have%20been%20responsible%20for%20underdevelopment%20in%20Bihar.%20Low%20human%20capital%20and%20lack%20of%20education%20and%20health%20are%20also%20responsible%20for%20low%20incomes.%20Together%20with%20this%2C%20Bihar%20could%20not%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20economic%20liberalisation%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20hence%20its%20workforce%20remained%20primarily%20dependent%20on%20agriculture%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ashmita%20Gupta%2C%20member-secretary%2C%20Asian%20Development%20Research%20Institute%2C%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20Bihar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20underdeveloped%20states%20in%20India%20stuck%20in%20a%20low%20growth%20and%20high%20poverty%20regime.%20There%20is%20no%20new%20information%20(in%20the%20survey)%20as%20any%20ranking%20of%20states%20shows%20Bihar%20rank%20lowest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20indicates%20Bihar's%20economy%20has%20been%20growing%20steadily%20at%20an%20average%20of%2010%20per%20cent%20or%20more%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20but%20its%20citizens%20remained%20mired%20in%20poverty.%20So%20where%20did%20all%20the%20growth%20and%20economic%20prosperity%20go%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20finding%20of%20the%20survey%20is%20that%20more%20than%2050%20lakh%20people%20from%20Bihar%20were%20living%20outside%20the%20state%20for%20livelihood%20or%20better%20education%20opportunities.%20The%20lack%20of%20non-farm%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20Bihar%20has%20compelled%20a%20large%20number%20of%20migrant%20workers%20to%20engage%20in%20short%20term%2C%20casual%20and%20precarious%20employment%20in%20other%20states.%20They%20live%20and%20work%20in%20unsafe%20and%20unhygienic%20conditions.%20Back%20home%2C%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20their%20families%20suffer%20from%20low%20and%20irregular%20remittances%20as%20well%20as%20political%20exclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20survey%20says%20only%2022.67%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20have%20studied%20till%20Class%205%2C%20but%20this%20increases%20to%2024.31%20per%20cent%20for%20people%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%2024.65%20per%20cent%20for%20those%20from%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs).%20Only%205.76%20per%20cent%20Scheduled%20Castes%20have%20finished%20Grades%2011%20and%2012.%20The%20Union%20Education%20Ministry%20too%20had%20highlighted%20that%20Bihar%20has%20the%20lowest%20literacy%20rate%20in%20India%20at%2061.8%20per%20cent%20(data%20shared%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202023).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar's%20education%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20a%20shambles.%20Primary%20education%20has%20only%20worsened%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20introduced%20a%20contract%20system%20for%20recruiting%20primary%20teachers%2C%20compromising%20talent%20and%20quality.%20Teachers%20with%20fake%20degrees%20have%20been%20employed%20in%20government%20schools.%20University%20and%20college%20teachers%20don't%20get%20their%20salary%20on%20time.%20Mushrooming%20below%20par%20private%20universities%20further%20cheat%20students%20in%20the%20name%20of%20education.%20According%20to%20the%20latest%20report%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Economic%20Survey%2C%20dropouts%20are%20a%20major%20problem%20that%20pervades%20all%20stages%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20would%20shoot%20down%20and%20discredit%20any%20negative%20data%20from%20central%20and%20other%20agencies.%20This%20time%20it%20is%20the%20state%20government's%20caste%20survey%2C%20carried%20out%20ostensibly%20to%20gain%20electoral%20mileage%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20elections.%20The%20government%20chooses%20not%20to%20care%20about%20the%20adverse%20impact%20as%20it%20seeks%20Dalit%2C%20OBC%20and%20EBC%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste-based%20political%20discourse%20in%20Bihar%20has%20had%20such%20power%20over%20the%20years%20that%20citizens%20have%20been%20blind%20to%20chronic%20poverty%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20irresolvable.%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20created%20the%20EBC%20constituency%20in%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%20hopes%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20new%20category%20as%20none%20of%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20has%20a%20state%20chief%20that%20belongs%20to%20this%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20already%20announced%20plans%20to%20conduct%20caste-based%20headcounts%20if%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power.%20The%20alliance%20also%20feels%20that%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20survey%20will%20burnish%20its%20%26quot%3Bpro-poor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpro-social%20justice%26quot%3B%20credentials.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20making%20inroads%20among%20the%20EBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20the%20opposition%20is%20trying%20to%20win%20back%20lost%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCaste%20is%20a%20medieval%20identity.%20The%20sooner%20it%20is%20dispensed%20with%2C%20the%20better.%20It%20is%20ironic%20that%20even%20the%20Left%2C%20which%20never%20spoke%20about%20caste%20but%20always%20took%20up%20issues%20of%20class%2C%20is%20now%20talking%20about%20caste.%20Even%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20talking%20more%20about%20caste.%20Congress%20too%20is%20openly%20talking%20about%20making%20caste%20a%20national%20agenda.%20None%20of%20the%20parties%20are%20giving%20any%20hope%20of%20socio-economic%20development.%20Eighty%20per%20cent%20of%20social%20injustice%20can%20be%20eradicated%20by%20addressing%20the%20question%20of%20economic%20injustice.%20Social%20reforms%20can%20further%20take%20care%20of%20solving%20the%20remaining%20twenty%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Professor%20N%20K%20Choudhary%2C%20former%20Head%20of%20Economics%20at%20the%20Patna%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20continuation%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20his%20caste%20-%20Kurmi%20-%20forming%20just%20three%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%2C%20will%20be%20difficult.%20At%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20counter%20this%20narrative%20of%20caste%20with%20religion%20and%20nothing%20will%20change%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Bihar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlas%2C%20neither%20mass%20leaders%20nor%20political%20parties%20in%20Bihar%20have%20development%20on%20their%20agenda.%20Caste%20politics%20has%20reaped%20dividends%20for%20parties%20since%20the%201990s%20because%20it%20appeals%20easily%20to%20masses%20who%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20prosperity%2C%20feel%20great%20pride%20in%20their%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist).%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699449000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Faevometo_nitish-kumar-1200_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbihars-caste-survey-and-its-intractable-poverty-challenge-4557802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Governments%20and%20netas%20since%20independence%20have%20failed%20Bihar.%20More%20than%20a%20third%20-%2034%20per%20cent%20-%20of%20families%20in%20Bihar%20live%20in%20poverty%2C%20surviving%20on%20Rs%206%2C000%20a%20month%20or%20less%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20tabled%20in%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbihars-caste-survey-and-its-intractable-poverty-challenge-4557802%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Agrochemical%20firm%20Best%20Agrolife%20Q2%20net%20profit%20falls%2027%20pc%20to%20Rs%2095%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699448980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F10%2Ffull%2F1686417861-0636.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2F