2%3Cp%3EAnti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20posted%20today%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20Ms%20Moitra%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20cash%20for%20query%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20Mr%20Dubey%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20lens%20of%20the%20Parliamentary%20Ethics%20Committee.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20he%20had%20demanded%20her%20immediate%20suspension%20from%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20basis%20of%20my%20complaint%2C%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20corruption%20that%20compromises%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20BJP%20MP's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishikant%20Dubey%20has%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20accepted%20cash%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%20on%20his%20behalf%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20business%20rival%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20by%20sharing%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20with%20the%20businessman%2C%20has%20compromised%20national%20security.%20In%20an%20explosive%20affidavit%2C%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20has%20admitted%20to%20the%20login%20sharing%2C%20but%20bypassed%20the%20cash%20for%20query%20issue%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20given%20Ms%20Moitra%20gifts%20that%20she%20had%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20that%20Ms%20Moitra's%20login%20has%20been%20used%20multiple%20times%20from%20Dubai%2C%20where%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20currently%20resides.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra%20has%20accepted%20that%20she%20shared%20her%20login%2C%20but%20claimed%20the%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20of%20that%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20shared%20with%20the%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20her%20hearing%20with%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20she%20had%20written%20them%20a%20letter%2C%20mentioning%20that%20there%20is%20no%20regulation%20governing%20sharing%20of%20login%20and%20password.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20were%20these%20rules%20not%20shared%20with%20MPs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20questioned%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20had%20stormed%20out%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20took%20place%20last%20week%2C%20accusing%20the%20committee%20of%20subjecting%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bproverbial%20vastraharan%20(stripping)%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ethics%20panel%20chief%20--%20BJP%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%20--%20has%20focussed%20on%20Ms%20Moitra's%20personal%20relationship%20with%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%20There%20were%20questions%20too%20on%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%2C%20on%20whose%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20the%20entire%20case%20rests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20has%20accused%20Ms%20Moitra%20of%20non-cooperation.%20%26quot%3BMahua%20Moitra%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20the%20committee%20and%20the%20investigation.%20The%20Opposition%20members%20also%20made%20allegations%20in%20anger%20and%20suddenly%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20to%20avoid%20answering%20more%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sonkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699446900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fkn3t4si_mahua-moitra_625x300_31_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-inquiry-against-mahua-moitra-ordered-by-anti-corruption-panel-bjp-mp-4557198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20posted%20today%20on%20X%2