%20roads%20in%20advance%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20improve%20road%20safety%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fwaze%2Fcrash-history-alerts-arrive-to-the-waze-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eannounced%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20blog%20post%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaze%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20FreeMap%20Israel%2C%20was%20founded%20in%202006%20and%20then%20acquired%20by%20Google%20for%20%241.3%20billion%20in%202013.%20It's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-waze%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecommunity-focused%20traffic%20and%20navigation%20app%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20provides%20real-time%20updates%20about%20hazards%2C%20accidents%2C%20speed%20cameras%2C%20and%20weather%20conditions%20based%20on%20data%20supplied%20by%20drivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20latest%20%26quot%3Bcrash%20history%20alerts%26quot%3B%20feature%20uses%20AI%20and%20reports%20from%20other%20drivers%20who%20use%20Waze%20to%20combine%20historical%20crash%20data%20and%20key%20information%20about%20a%20route%20such%20as%20its%20usual%20traffic%20levels%20or%20whether%20it's%20a%20highway%20or%20local%20road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20route%20has%20a%20history%20of%20accidents%2C%20the%20driver%20will%20be%20warned%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20before%20they%20reach%20that%20part%20of%20their%20journey%20so%20they%20can%20plan%20ahead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Waze%2C%20won't%20show%20as%20many%20alerts%20on%20roads%20drivers%20regularly%20navigate%2C%20saying%20the%20extra%20alerts%20could%20pose%20a%20distraction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaze%20is%20focused%20on%20social%20interactions%20between%20drivers%20and%20allows%20users%20to%20chat%20directly%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20comment%20on%20road%20incidents%20on%20the%20map%2C%20and%20even%20lets%20you%20connect%20to%20music%20streaming%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20lets%20users%20earn%20points%20and%20graduate%20different%20levels%20from%20Waze%20baby%2C%20Wazer%2C%20Waze%20Knight%2C%20and%20Waze%20Royalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoad%20traffic%20crashes%20are%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20death%20globally%20and%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Finjury%2Ffeatures%2Fglobal-road-safety%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20CDC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Almost%203%2C700%20people%20are%20killed%20everyday%20in%20crashes%20involving%20vehicles%20like%20cars%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20motorcycle%20and%20its%20the%20eighth%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-waze-alerts-drivers-about-accident-crash-prone-roads-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699446876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654b75383cc84b4dfafe6092%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-waze-alerts-drivers-about-accident-crash-prone-roads-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waze%20will%20combine%20historical%20crash%20data%20and%20key%20information%20about%20a%20route%20such%20as%20its%20usual%20traffic%20levels%20to%20determine%20whether%20to%20alert%20drivers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogles-waze-alerts-drivers-about-accident-crash-prone-roads-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Large%20pickup%20trucks%20not%20very%20safe%20for%20backseat%20passengers%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699446606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105071285%2Cimgsize-1082237.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatim