C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Pasi%20(1%2C288%2C031%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20humans%20can%20be%20identified%20from%20their%20clothes%20or%20other%20such%20identity%20markers%20is%20a%20question%20which%20has%20both%20political%20and%20non-political%20connotations%20in%20the%20present%20times.%20While%20it%20might%20be%20easy%20to%20distinguish%20a%20Brahmin%20from%20a%20Muslim%2C%20can%20one%20identify%20the%20caste%20of%20a%20person%20simply%20by%20looking%20at%20their%20clothes%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20well-known%20couplet%2C%20mystic%20poet%20Kabir%20once%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20good%20is%20it%20being%20tall%20like%20a%20date%20palm%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20has%20no%20shade%20to%20offer%20to%20a%20traveller%20and%20the%20fruits%20are%20beyond%20reach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20palm%20tree%20and%20dates%20which%20Kabir%20spoke%20of%20in%20this%20couplet%20are%20indispensable%20for%20the%20caste%20group%20we%20are%20going%20to%20talk%20about%20here.%20This%20is%20a%20caste%20group%20whose%20members%20can%20be%20identified%20very%20easily%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20black%20marks%20on%20their%20hands%2C%20chest%20and%20legs.%20They%20are%20the%20Pasi%20people%2C%20who%20climb%20the%20high-reaching%20palm%20trees%20and%20bring%20down%20toddy.%20Toddy%20is%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20beverage%20which%20was%20turned%20into%20an%20intoxicating%20substance%20by%20man.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20412px)%2085vw%2C%20412px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22590%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKabir%20was%20not%20a%20Pasi%20but%20hailed%20from%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebunkar%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eweaver%20family.%20Muslim%20weavers%20were%20called%20Julaha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20similarity%20between%20a%20Pasi%20and%20Julaha.%20Like%20traditional%20weavers%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Pasi%20caste%20group%20also%20weave.%20They%20not%20only%20weave%20mats%20from%20palm%20leaves%2C%20but%20also%20weave%20roofs%20for%20huts.%20Times%20may%20have%20changed%20but%20some%20things%20are%20still%20the%20same%20like%20hand-made%20fans%20made%20of%20palm%20which%20are%20used%20even%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPasi%20is%20categorised%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20etc.%20But%20an%20essential%20criterion%20for%20being%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20is%20that%20only%20%E2%80%98untouchables%E2%80%99%20are%20included%20in%20this%20category.%20It%20raises%20a%20question%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20traditional%20profession%20of%20this%20caste.%20Even%20today%20in%20the%20villages%20of%20Bihar%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Pasi%20community%20are%20not%20considered%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20serving%20toddy%20to%20the%20people.%20In%20the%20villages%2C%20toddy%20drinking%20takes%20place%20amidst%20palm%20trees%2C%20where%20people%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20communities%20gather%20to%20drink%20together.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20question%20of%20being%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20becomes%20secondary%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20economic%20condition%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20has%20undoubtedly%20depended%20on%20palm%20trees%2C%20but%20not%20entirely.%20Since%20most%20of%20them%20do%20not%20possess%20agricultural%20land%2C%20they%20earn%20their%20living%20by%20working%20as%20farm%20labourers.%20But%20they%20are%20treated%20with%20disdain%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20beverage%20which%20they%20bring%20down%20from%20the%20trees%20with%20great%20difficulty%20and%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20their%20lives%20has%20been%20described%20in%20the%20Vedas%20as%20%E2%80%98preferred%20by%20the%20gods%E2%80%99.%20In%20his%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Myth%20of%20Holy%20Cow%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20famous%20historian%20D.N.%20Jha%20discussed%20how%20Hindu%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20drank%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20name%20of%20a%20god%2C%20Soma%2C%20appears%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EVeda%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20tree%20bearing%20the%20same%20name%20in%20one%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erichas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EVedic%20psalms.%20According%20to%20the%20Vedas%2C%20an%20intoxicant%20is%20obtained%20from%20this%20tree%20and%20the%20gods%20gave%20the%20responsibility%20of%20fetching%20it%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Pasi%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnthropological%20Survey%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Kumar%20Suresh%20Singh%20and%20B.V.%20Bhanu%20have%20explained%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20word%20Pasi%20as%20well.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20one%20etymology%20of%20the%20word%20Pasi%20can%20be%20traced%20to%20the%20Sanskrit%20term%20Pashika.%20But%20neither%20this%20book%20nor%20any%20other%20explains%20how%20it%20changed%20from%20%E2%80%98Pashika%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98Pasi%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Pasi%20caste%20group%20has%20its%20own%20history%20too.%20It%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Pasi%20community%20used%20to%20rule%20the%20area%20of%20Awadh%20once.%20Lucknow%2C%20which%20was%20called%20the%20city%20of%20Nawabs%2C%20was%20actually%20the%20capital%20of%20Lakhan%20Pasi.%20In%20addition%2C%20descriptions%20of%20Ganga%20Bux%20Rawat%2C%20Maharaja%20Bijli%20Pasi%2C%20Maharaja%20Suheldev%20Pasi%2C%20Chhita%20Pasi%2C%20Satan%20Pasi%2C%20Aman%20Rajpiyu%20Japla%2C%20Madari%20Pasi%20and%20Uda%20Devi%20Pasi%20also%20appear%20in%20historical%20accounts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20history%20of%20Bihar%2C%20no%20one%20can%20deny%20the%20contribution%20of%20Jaglal%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Chhapra%20district.%20His%20father%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20Musan%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20was%20illiterate%20and%20used%20to%20sell%20toddy%2C%20and%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20Tetri%20Devi.%20His%20brother%20was%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20British%20army%20%E2%80%93%20which%20helped%20Jaglal%20get%20educated.%20In%201914%2C%20he%20went%20to%20study%20at%20the%20Medical%20College%20of%20Calcutta.%20In%201921%2C%20at%20the%20call%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20quit%20studies%20and%20forayed%20into%20politics.%20He%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20interim%20government%20formed%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20year%201937.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20later%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20excise%20and%20public%20health%20department.%20The%20chief%20minister%20was%20Krishna%20Singh%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20hardly%20anyone%20is%20aware%20that%20it%20was%20Jaglal%20Chaudhary%20who%20had%20announced%20prohibition%20in%20the%20state%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20became%20the%20minister.%20Although%20it%20was%20not%20implemented%20in%20the%20entire%20state%2C%20its%20implementation%20was%20100%25%20in%20Chhapra%2C%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Hazaribagh%20and%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20population%20of%20the%20Pasi%20caste%20in%20Bihar%20is%201%2C288%2C031%2C%20which%20is%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%20It%20is%20clearly%20not%20an%20easy%20task%20for%20a%20caste%20with%20such%20a%20small%20populace%20to%20carve%20a%20decisive%20niche%20in%20a%20democracy%20based%20on%20numbers.%20The%20current%20politico-social%20equation%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260208%2Fbihar-caste-survey-what-is-the-history-of-chaupal-caste%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-cast