lty%20(95.7)%2C%20among%20other%20indicators.%20IIT%20Bombay's%20staff%20with%20PhD%20stood%20out%20as%20its%20strongest%20indicator.%20Additionally%2C%20IIT%20Bombay%20is%20ranked%20149%20in%20the%20QS%20World%20Rankings%202024.%20The%20top%20five%20positions%20in%20the%20QS%20World%20University%20Rankings%202024%20are%20held%20by%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Cambridge%20University%2C%20Oxford%20University%2C%20Harvard%20University%2C%20and%20Stanford%20University%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeking%20University%20is%20the%20top-ranked%20institution%20in%20Asia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeking%20University%20in%20China%20secured%20the%20top%20position%20in%20Asia%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20and%20Tsinghua%20University.%20Among%20the%20top%2010%2C%20China%20is%20represented%20by%20four%20institutions%2C%20while%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20and%20Singapore%20each%20have%20two%20universities%20in%20the%20QS%20Asia%20University%20Rankings%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699443840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-07%2Fiit-bombay_650x400_71468227352.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-leads-indian-institutions-in-qs-asia-university-rankings-2024-4557382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22QS%20Asia%20University%20Rankings%202024%3A%20IIT%20Bombay%20received%20an%20overall%20score%20of%2067.2%20out%20of%20100%2C%20excelling%20in%20academic%20reputation%20(83.5)%20and%20employer%20reputation%20(96).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-leads-indian-institutions-in-qs-asia-university-rankings-2024-4557382%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fiit-bombay-le