ll%2C%20as%20in%20duty%20bound%2C%20honestly%20and%20faithfully%20serve%20in%20the%20regular%20Army%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20and%20go%20wherever%20ordered%20by%20land%2C%20sea%20or%20air%2C%20and%20that%20I%20will%20observe%20and%20obey%20all%20commands%20of%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20and%20the%20commands%20of%20any%20officer%20set%20over%20me%20even%20to%20the%20peril%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20the%20soldier%E2%80%99s%20obedience%20is%20to%20the%20president%20of%20India%20and%20his%20loyalty%20is%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20serving%20soldier%20is%20governed%20by%20military%20law%20in%20addition%20to%20every%20other%20law%20which%20governs%20every%20citizen%2C%20certain%20fundamental%20rights%20available%20to%20every%20citizen%20are%20denied%20to%20him%20by%20Section%2021%20of%20the%20Army%20Act%20and%20the%20Army%20Rules%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20duties%20performed%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20regular%20Army%20and%20for%20the%20maintenance%20of%20discipline%20among%20them%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Specifically%2C%20Army%20Rule%2020%20prohibits%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20and%20non-military%20activities%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20the%20command%20structure%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces%20has%20preserved%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20professional%20conduct%20and%20performance%2C%20and%20the%20apolitical%20character%20of%20the%20serving%20soldier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20in%201932%2C%20a%20Field%20Marshal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fveterans-letter-secular-indian-army%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadvised%20young%20Indian%20Army%20officers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyoung%20Indian%20man%20of%20education%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20seems%20very%20attracted%20by%20politics.%20May%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20remember%20that%20politics%20do%20not%2C%20and%20cannot%2C%20find%20any%20place%20in%20army%20life.%20An%20army%20can%20have%20no%20place%20in%20politics.%20Once%20there%20is%20any%20suspicion%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20Army%2C%20or%20any%20part%20of%20it%2C%20is%20biased%20politically%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20from%20that%20moment%20that%20Army%20has%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20nation%20which%20pays%20for%20it.%20It%20is%20no%20longer%20impartial%2C%20and%20that%20way%20lies%20chaos%20and%20civil%20war%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPublic%20trust%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%202019%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-most-trusted-political-parties-least-public-opinion-survey%2Fstory-8t70KC3jRHCHONwblQBgMK.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurvey%20of%20public%20opinion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20relating%20to%20politics%2C%20society%2C%20and%20governance%2C%20revealed%20that%20people%20trust%20the%20Army%20the%20most%2C%20with%20the%20judiciary%20next.%20The%20least%20trusted%20are%20the%20police%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20and%20political%20parties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20public%20recognises%20the%20apolitical%20nature%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces%2C%20as%20a%20criterion%20for%20trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-services-armed-forces-propaganda-india-failed-state%5C%22%3ECommandeering%20Civil%20Services%20and%20Armed%20Forces%20for%20Propaganda%20Could%20Make%20India%20a%20Failed%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESoldiers%20on%20leave%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Army%20has%20the%20legacy%20problem%20of%20short-staffing%20of%20officers%2C%20and%20post-COVID-19%2C%20among%20personnel%20below%20officer%20rank.%20The%20Army%20has%20maintained%20operational%20capability%20and%20readiness%2C%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20increased%20stress%20during%20active%20service.%20It%20is%20established%20that%20stress%20is%20a%20prime%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereason%20for%20suicide%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20among%20troops.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELeave%20is%20a%20de-stressing%2C%20precious%20time%20away%20from%20the%20extreme%20rigours%20of%20service%2C%20when%20soldiers%20spend%20quality%20time%20with%20family%20and%20attend%20to%20matters%20that%20spouses%20were%20unable%20to%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEnsuring%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20leave%20is%20a%20responsibility%20of%20military%20commanders%2C%20essential%20for%20individual%20and%20unit%20morale%2C%20far%20more%20than%20a%20welfare%20measure%20or%20part%20of%20terms%20of%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20well-understood%20situation%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20Headquarters%20directed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20although%20the%20word%20used%20is%20%E2%80%9Crecommended%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cevery%20soldier%20proceeding%20on%20leave%20volunteers%20to%20choose%20any%20subject%2Fdomain%20as%20per%20own%20interest%2Fcompetency%20and%20the%20felt%20need%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20local%20community%2C%20and%20engages%20citizens%2C%20thereby%20making%20an%20individual%20contribution%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20nation-building%20effort%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShort-staffed%20units%20are%20to%20provide%20soldiers%20with%20literature%2C%20to%20use%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%E2%80%9D%20efforts%20on%20social%2C%20civic%20and%20patriotic%20themes%2C%20such%20as%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%2C%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%2C%20etc.%20The%20unit%20will%20monitor%20compliance%20using%20photographs%20and%20videos%20which%20the%20soldier%20takes.%20Pressure%20to%20comply%20will%20cause%20stress%20during%20leave%2C%20and%20anxiety%20on%20return%20to%20duty%20station%2C%20perhaps%20defeating%20the%20purpose%20of%20leave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20soldier-on-leave%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntarily%E2%80%9D%20promoting%20government%20schemes%20can%20be%20negative%20for%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20morale%20and%20functioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShowcasing%20performance%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20directed%20defence%20establishments%20to%20set%20up%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-selfie-points-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E822%20geo-tagged%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20nine%20cities%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%20good%20works%20done%20in%20defence%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cattract%20public%20attention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20armed%20forces%20are%20to%20set%20up%20and%20operationalise%20100%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20under%20government-defined%20themes%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Atmanirbhar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%E2%80%99%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Sashaktikaran%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20send%20%E2%80%9Caction%20taken%20reports%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%2C%20using%20the%20armed%20forces%20to%20promote%20and%20advertise%20government%20policies%2C%20has%20an%20obvious%20political%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154708%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.46.47-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154708%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.46.47-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154708%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.46.47-PM-300x180.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154708%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.46.47-PM-1024x613.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20selfie%20point%20at%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECivil-military%20relations%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces%20are%20subordinate%20to%20control%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20the%20day.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20should%20consult%20the%20service%20chiefs%20(or%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff)%20before%20issuing%20directions%20such%20as%20soldiers-on-leave%20%E2%80%9Cvolunteering%E2%80%9D%20to%20promote%20government%20schemes%2C%20or%20establish%20%E2%80%9Cselfie-points%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20same%20purpose%2C%20because%20they%20impact%20the%20soldier%20and%20the%20service.%20It%20will%20never%20be%20known%20whether%20the%20government%20consulted%20the%20four-star%20top%20brass%2C%20or%20if%20consulted%2C%20what%20they%20advised%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20earlier%2C%20the%20four-star%20top%20brass%20had%20complied%20with%20directions%20to%20arrange%20yoga%20mats%20on%20Raj%20Path%20(2015)%20for%20the%20government%20to%20set%20a%20world%20record%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cntraveller.in%2Fstory%2Fdear-tourists-the-indian-army-is-picking-up-your-trash%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclear%20garbage%20thrown%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Himalayan%20pilgrimage%20tourists%20(2017).%20Both%20these%20tasks%20were%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20duty%20and%20competence%20of%20other%20agencies.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGetting%20soldiers%20to%20do%20such%20tasks%20indicates%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20step-motherly%20attitude%20towards%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Other%20examples%20are%3A%20death%20and%20disability%20benefits%20to%20soldiers%20made%20lower%20than%20for%20their%20civilian%20counterparts%3B%20denying%20non-functional%20financial%20up-gradation%20(NFU)%20to%20the%20armed%20forces%20although%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%20receive%20it%3B%20and%20delaying%20the%20payment%20of%20OROP%20arrears%20ordered%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPoliticisation%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20military%20top%20brass%20to%20convince%20the%20political%20leadership%20to%20not%20pass%20orders%20which%20are%20political%20in%20nature%20and%20intent%2C%20or%20impact%20adversely%20on%20the%20soldier%20and%20the%20service%2C%20and%20thereby%20on%20national%20security.%20This%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done%20in%20the%20best%20of%20times%2C%20but%20under%20the%20present%20dispensation%2C%20it%20is%20much%20more%20difficult.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20difficulty%2C%20when%20the%20military%20leadership%20fails%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20get%20politicised%20by%20default.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csoldier-volunteer%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cselfie-point%E2%80%9D%20initiatives%20for%20political%20purposes%20are%20measures%20which%20politicise%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20since%20the%20government%20cannot%20be%20unaware%20of%20the%20Army%20Act%20and%20Army%20Rules%2C%20which%20prohibit%20political%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20military%20veterans%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20deleterious%20long-term%20impact%20of%20politics%20on%20the%20morale%20and%20cohesion%20of%20our%20armed%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECentral%20and%20state%20governments%20prepare%20development%20plans%20and%20schemes%20to%20benefit%20the%20people%2C%20but%20advertising%20them%20is%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20agenda.%20Soldiers%20promoting%20government%20schemes%20is%20unambiguously%20political%20activity.%20When%20it%20is%20ordered%20by%20the%20highest%20military%20authority%20in%20compliance%20with%20government%20directives%2C%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailypioneer.com%2F2023%2Fcolumnists%2Fpoliticisation-of-army--no-pros--only-cons.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epoliticises%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20armed%20forces.%20The%20g%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eovernment%20would%20do%20well%20to%20cease%20using%20the%20Army%20for%20political%20purposes%2C%20and%20the%20military%20top%20brass%20would%20do%20well%20to%20maintain%20the%20apolitical%20nature%20of%20the%20soldier%20and%20the%20service%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsvombat%5C%22%3EMajor%20General%20S.G.%20Vombatkere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20VSM%20retired%20as%20additional%20DG%20(Discipline%20%26amp%3B%20Vigilance)%20in%20the%20Army%20HQ%20AG%E2%80%99