ing%20their%20future%20in%20the%20competition.%20While%20the%20situations%20could%20not%20be%20further%20apart%20for%20the%20traditional%20rivals%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20solid%20chance%20that%20they%20can%20end%20up%20facing%20each%20other%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20semifinals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20guaranteed%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%20final%20points%20table%20irrespective%20of%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20game%20against%20the%20Netherlands.%20India%20have%2016%20points%20from%208%20matches%20and%20second-placed%20South%20Africa%20are%20at%2014%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Pakistan%20can%20secure%204th%20spot%20in%20Points%20Table%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20to%20win%20their%20last%20match%20and%20depend%20on%20Afghanistan%20and%20hope%20to%20get%20a%20favourable%20result%20from%20the%20New%20Zealand%20game%20to%20book%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20semifinals.%20Pakistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%20have%20one%20match%20left%20in%20the%20tournament%20while%20Afghanistan%20will%20play%20South%20Africa%20in%20their%20final%20game%20in%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20already%20lost%20against%20Australia%2C%20if%20Afghanistan%20lose%20against%20South%20Africa%20too%2C%20the%20race%20will%20come%20down%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%20provided%20they%20win%20their%20respective%20matches.%20If%20Afghanistan%20win%20against%20South%20Africa%2C%20all%20three%20teams%20will%20have%2010%20points%20(provided%20Pakistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%20win%20their%20respective%20final%20matches%20too)%2C%20and%20the%20race%20for%20the%204th%20spot%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20(NRR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Pakistan%20win%20their%20match%20and%20both%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Afghanistan%20lose%20their%20final%20matches%20in%20the%20group%20stage%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplay