n%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3EIndians%20who%20received%20warnings%20from%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%2031%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%20may%20be%20targeting%20their%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Apple%20did%20not%20say%20which%20state%20may%20have%20sponsored%20the%20attacks%2C%20the%20profiles%20of%20those%20targeted%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20some%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20led%20to%20suspicion%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20was%20behind%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMangnale%20is%20South%20Asia%20editor%20for%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20a%20global%20network%20of%20investigative%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20fellow%20OCCRP%20journalists%20Ravi%20Nair%20and%20N.B.R.%20Arcadio%2C%20Mangnale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Ereported%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20used%20opaque%20offshore%20funds%20based%20in%20Mauritius%20to%20inflate%20the%20valuation%20of%20its%20group%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20OCCRP%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20the%20investors%3Cb%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eturned%20out%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Cwidely%20reported%20ties%20to%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20majority%20shareholders%2C%20the%20Adani%20family%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20is%20perceived%20as%20having%20benefited%20from%20close%20ties%20his%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20co-founder%20Drew%20Sullivan%20told%20Reuters%20that%20the%20use%20of%20Pegasus%20on%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%20and%20outrageous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20government%20is%20spying%20on%20the%20reporters%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20plausible%20explanation%20for%20that%20other%20than%20political%20gain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-pegasus-journalists-ministers-activists-phones-spying%5C%22%3Ehas%20used%20Pegasus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20made%20by%20Israeli%20cybersecurity%20firm%20NSO%20Group%2C%20against%20its%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsers%20of%20the%20spyware%20are%20able%20to%20remotely%20hack%20into%20smartphones%20and%20gain%20access%20to%20their%20contents%20and%20functions%2C%20including%20the%20microphone%20and%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20neither%20confirmed%20nor%20denied%20its%20use%20of%20Pegasus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20during%20Supreme%20Court%20arguments%20in%202021%20that%20that%20the%20government%20cannot%20be%20made%20to%20answer%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20uses%20the%20spyware%20for%20this%20would%20alert%20terrorists%20and%20compromise%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20noted%20that%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-orders-formation-of-independent-expert-committee-to-probe-pegasus-project-revelations%5C%22%3Eabsence%20of%20any%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20denial%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20use%20of%20Pegasus%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20court%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20set%20up%20an%20independent%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20then-Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20N.V.%20Ramana%20noted%20in%20August%20last%20year%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-pegasus-technical-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20cooperate%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699434618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F23171618%2FScreen-Shot-2021-07-23-at-5.15.59-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fanand-mangnale-occrp-likely-had-pegasus-on-phone-report-says%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anand%20Mangnale%2C%20the%20journalist%20in%20question%2C%20was%20also%20warned%20by%20Apple%20last%20month%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%20may%20be%20targeting%20his%20iPhone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fanand-mangnale-occrp-likely-had-pegasus-on-phone-report-says%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brookfield%20India%20REIT%20Q2%20net%20operating%20income%20up%2044%25%20to%20Rs%20346.7%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699434601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-11%2F07%2Ffull%2F1667830828-0316.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbrookfield-india-reit-q2-net-operating-income-up-44-to-rs-346-7-crore-123110700873_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Income%20from%20operating%20lease%20rentals%20increased%20by%2033%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%20274.1%20crore%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20fiscal%2C%20from%20Rs%20205.6%20crore%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbrookfield-india-reit-q2-net-operating-income-up-44-to-rs-346-7-crore-123110700873_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbrookfield-india-reit-q2-net-operating-income-up-44-to-rs-346-7-crore-123110700873_1.html%22%2C%22amp