alnourished%20body%20to%20cause%20repeated%20pregnancies%20or%20talking%20about%20ways%20that%20she%20can%20avoid%20such%20a%20fate%20even%20when%20society%20and%20the%20government%20have%20failed%20in%20their%20duty%20to%20help%20her%20access%20contraception%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20are%20important%20when%20large%20sections%20of%20even%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberated%E2%80%9D%20are%20outraged%20over%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20description%20of%20withdrawal%20as%20one%20of%20the%20means%20that%20an%20educated%20woman%20can%20make%20her%20husband%20practice%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20unwanted%20pregnancies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiggling%20and%20blushing%20MLAs%20all%20around%20him%20%E2%80%93%20Kumar%20himself%20succumbs%20to%20a%20fit%20of%20laughter%20for%20a%20while%20%E2%80%93%20contribute%20to%20the%20trivialisation%20of%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESex%20is%20a%20taboo%20word%20in%20a%20country%20that%20produces%2025%20million%20children%20every%20year.%20Safe%20sex%20is%20anathema.%20Talking%20about%20it%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20sacrilege!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(data%20from%202019-20)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FIndia.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20only%2066.7%25%20Indian%20women%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20and%20just%2056.5%25%20have%20access%20to%20a%20modern%20method.%20(A%20modern%20method%20refers%20to%20sterilisation%2C%20contraceptive%20pills%2C%20condoms%2C%20intrauterine%20devices%20or%20injectable%20contraceptives.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FBihar.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBihar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20numbers%20are%2055.8%25%20for%20any%20method%20and%2044.4%25%20for%20any%20modern%20method.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20description%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20of%20withdrawal%2C%20a%20method%20where%20the%20man%20retracts%20before%20ejaculation.%20It%20is%20an%20accepted%20mode%20of%20contraception%20in%20any%20basic%20physiology%20textbook%2C%20albeit%20an%20unreliable%20one.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20fertility%20rate%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20the%20average%20number%20of%20children%20that%20a%20woman%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20during%20her%20life%20time%20%E2%80%93%20stands%20according%20to%20NFHS%205%20at%203%20in%20Bihar%20while%20the%20national%20average%20stands%20at%202.2%20which%20is%20just%20a%20notch%20above%20the%20replacement%20fertility%20rate%20of%202.1.%20Replacement%20fertility%20refers%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20population%20stops%20actually%20growing%20as%20death%20and%20birth%20rates%20reach%20a%20balance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20times%20immemorial%20governments%20in%20India%20have%20made%20family%20planning%20%E2%80%93%20euphemism%20for%20reducing%20births%20%E2%80%93%20their%20business.%20Yet%20if%2033%25%20Indian%20women%20and%2045%25%20Bihari%20women%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20that%20should%20be%20the%20cause%20for%20real%20outrage%20for%20all.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20squeamishness%20to%20talk%20about%20sex%20and%20the%20political%20backlash%20that%20anything%20akin%20to%20sex%20education%20invariably%20generates%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20Indian%20men%20get%20their%20sex%20education%20from%20pornography%20materials%20and%20women%20largely%20get%20it%20from%20life%2C%20learning%20the%20hard%20way%20about%20what%20can%20cause%20a%20pregnancy%20often%20ending%20up%20as%20unwitting%20victims%20of%20a%20system%20that%20is%20quick%20to%20punish%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnmet%20contraceptive%20needs%20lead%20to%20illegal%20abortions%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20contraception%20and%20sex%20education%20go%20beyond%20the%20need%20of%20limiting%20family%20size%20which%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20multilayered%20proposition%20with%20implications%20on%20health%2C%20education%2C%20economic%20status%20etc%20of%20a%20family.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20life%20and%20death.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20seminal%20book%20%3Cem%3EPutting%20Women%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20based%20on%20her%20own%20gynaecology%20practice%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20Bang%20gives%20innumerable%20examples%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20them%20as%20young%20as%2013%20%E2%80%93%20getting%20pregnant%20within%20weeks%20of%20menarche%2C%20sometimes%20not%20realising%20that%20they%20are%20pregnant%20till%20its%20too%20late%20to%20abort%20and%20then%20victimised%20by%20the%20tribal%20society%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cmistakes%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20telling%20statement%20on%20what%20lack%20of%20sex%20education%20does%20to%20young%20people%2C%20Dr%20Bang%20recounts%20the%20tale%20of%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20wrote%20her%20a%20letter%20addressing%20her%20as%20%E2%80%9Cauntie%E2%80%9D%20to%20talk%20about%20his%20own%20adolescent%20sexual%20insecurities%20and%20of%20a%20married%20couple%20who%20arrived%20at%20her%20clinic%20unsure%20about%20what%20constitutes%20the%20sexual%20act.%20She%20recounts%20countless%20cases%20in%20great%20detail%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20who%20had%20landed%20up%20at%20her%20clinic%20demanding%20an%20abortion%20past%20the%20legal%20timelines%20and%20then%20ending%20up%20either%20with%20an%20illegal%20abortion%20or%20worse%20still%20delivering%20an%20unwanted%20baby%20that%20is%20buried%20alive%20as%20per%20local%20practices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund%20(UNFPA)%E2%80%99s%20State%20of%20the%20World%20Population%20Report%202022.%20Between%202007-2011%2C%2067%25%20of%20abortions%20in%20India%20were%20classified%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-unintended-pregnancy-abortion-7845655%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunsafe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Many%20of%20them%20happen%20first%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20contraceptive%20access%20and%20awareness%2C%20then%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20safe%20(and%20non%20judgemental)%20abortion%20facilities.%20Every%20day%20an%20estimated%208%20women%20die%20in%20India%20because%20of%20unsafe%20abortions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Bang%20is%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%C2%A0%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearchforhealth.ngo%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESociety%20for%20Education%2C%20Action%20and%20Research%20in%20Community%20Health%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(SEARCH)%20which%20runs%20a%20100%20bed%20hospital%20in%20Gadchiroli%20and%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20many%20public%20health%20initiatives%20that%20have%20over%20the%20years%20been%20integrated%20into%20national%20programmes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20women%20are%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20contraception%20and%20often%20at%20a%20loss%20about%20how%20to%20access%20it%20was%20evident%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Finjectable-contraceptives-at-mewat-women-get-shot-of-empowerment-5417216%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMewat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20categorised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20backward%20districts%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20immediately%20after%20the%20inclusion%20of%20injectable%20contraceptives%20in%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20basket%20saw%20women%20turning%20up%20at%20the%20clinics%20for%20a%20shot%2C%20often%20without%20telling%20their%20families.%20The%20women%20told%20me%20they%20wanted%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20cycle%20of%20annual%20pregnancies%20in%20which%20many%20of%20them%20were%20caught%20and%20as%20the%20local%20health%20workers%20talked%20to%20them%20about%20options%2C%20that%20of%20getting%20a%20shot%20that%20would%20prevent%20pregnancies%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20was%20a%20godsend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20assembly%20gives%20women%20access%20to%20one%20more%20method%20of%20contraception%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20rudimentary%20and%20primitive%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20a%20few%20laughs.%20The%20outrage%20can%20be%20reserved%20for%20more%20deserving%20causes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20author.%20She%20currently%20works%20with%20Chase%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699432843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02190722%2FNitish-Kumar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trivialisation%20of%20this%20issue%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ethics%20Panel's%20Next%20Meeting%20Date%20Ensures%20Another%20Non-BJP%20Member%20Can't%20Attend'%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F04145325%2F2022_2img03_Feb_2022_PTI02_03_2022_000159B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Two%20days%20before%20the%20parliament%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20ethics%20committee%20is%20to%20meet%20to%20consider%20adopting%20its%20%E2%80%98draft%20report%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20she%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20when%20it%20meets%20this%20November%209%2C%20its%20composition%20will%20be%20tilted%20even%20further%20towards%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20allegation%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20that%20Moitra%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20forwarded%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee.%20This%20also%20meant%20he%20had%20to%20constitute%20the%20committee%20as%20it%20was%20not%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBirla%20formed%20a%2015-member%20committee%2C%20naming%20seven%20members%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20one%20from%20the%20pro-BJP%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20three%20from%20Congress%20and%20one%20each%20from%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20The%20committee%20was%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20has%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20committee%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20complaint%20filed%20against%20the%20opposition%20MP%20who%20has%20not%20only%20been%20a%20vociferous%20critic%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20but%20had%20also%20openly%20accused%20the%20complainant%20Dubey%20some%20time%20ago%20of%20submitting%20what%20she%20claimed%20was%20a%20fake%20degree%20along%20with%20his%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Moitra%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20Dubey%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20her%20because%20she%20inquired%20about%20his%20degree.%20The%20BJP%20MP%20has%20filed%20the%20complaint%20along%20with%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20whom%20Moitra%20has%20termed%20as%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Ejilted%20ex%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20the%20reason%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20targeting%20her%20is%20because%20she%20has%20been%20asking%20the%20Modi%20government%20several%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20its%20alleged%20favouritism%20towards%20the%20Gujarati%20business%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20Sonkar%20has%20picked%20November%209%20as%20the%20date%20for%20the%20ethics%20committee%20meeting%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Telangana%2C%20is%20unable%20to%20attend%20it.%20The%20MP%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20forthcoming%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20to%20be%20in%20his%20constituency%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20papers%20on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%2C%20five%20Opposition%20MPs%20including%20Reddy%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20chairperson%20asking%20Moitra%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Eindecent%20questions%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Moitra%20too%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20at%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20which%20she%20said%20was%20equal%20to%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3EVastraharan%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20had%20put%20in%20her%20request%20to%20the%20chairperson%20to%20cross-examine%20both%20Dehadrai%20and%20Hiranandani%20who%20had%20submitted%20a%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20affidavit%20to%20the%20committee%20claiming%20he%20had%20accessed%20her%20official%20email%20account%20to%20post%20parliamentary%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-ramesh-bidhuri-very-different-parliament-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Very%20Different%20Approach%20for%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Writes%20to%20Parliament%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20social%20media%2C%20Moitra%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20though%20the%20chairperson%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20November%209%20meeting%20would%20consider%20adopting%20a%20draft%20report%20on%20the%20complaint%2C%20no%20such%20report%20has%20been%20circulated%20among%20the%20members%20yet.%20She%20also%20added%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3EBJP%20calling%20allies%20to%20ensure%20attendance%20to%20adopt%20(the%20draft%20report)%20via%20majority.%20Chartered%20flight%20to%20fly%20in%20MP(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20state%20president%20(V.%20D.%20Sharma).%20How%20scared%20Adani%20%26amp%3B%20Modi%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey%20also%20took%20to%20X%20to%20claim%20that%20it%20was%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eguilty%20conscience%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20led%20her%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20panel%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-case-ethics-panel-likely-to-recommend-strict-actions-including-disqualification-of-tmc-mp-11699233232862.html%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20is%20likely%20to%20recommend%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Estrict%20actions%E2%80%9D%20including%20her%20suspension%20from%20parliament%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20decision%20by%20the%20committee%20would%20need%20to%20be%20endorsed%20by%20the%20speaker%20and%20would%20