20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Faligarh-may-soon-be-renamed-harigarh-resolution-passed-in-civic-body-meeting%2Farticleshow%2F105052570.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20The%20Mainpuri%20district%20council%20had%20sought%20to%20rename%20Mainpuri%20to%20Mayan%20Nagar.%20According%20to%20the%20Mainpuri%20district%20council%20president%2C%20the%20district%20was%20originally%20founded%20by%20the%20sage%20Mayan%20hence%20it%20should%20be%20renamed%20as%20Mayan%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20renaming%20of%20these%20two%20districts%20is%20set%20to%20join%20a%20long%20list%20of%20name%20changes%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%202018%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fhow-much-will-it-cost-to-rename-india-to-bharat-rs-14000-crore-2676833%5C%22%3EAllahabad%20was%20renamed%20as%20Prayagraj%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Feducation-today%2Fgk-current-affairs%2Fstory%2Fmughalsarai-station-renamed-1306483-2018-08-06%5C%22%3E156-year-old%20Mughalsarai%20junction%20was%20renamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Pandit%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyaya%20junction.%20In%202021%2C%20Faizabad%20was%20renamed%20as%20Ayodhya%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Adityanath%20had%20indicated%20that%20his%20government%20will%20continue%20renaming%20places%20across%20the%20state%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fproposal-to-change-the-name-of-aligarh-to-harigarh-passed%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20renaming%20of%20these%20places%20has%20subsequently%20led%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20for%20the%20renaming%20of%20various%20cities%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20In%20Agra%2C%20a%20lawmaker%20has%20proposed%20changing%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20name%20to%20Agravan%20