Bolero%20carrying%20five%20individuals(2%20women%20and%203%20men)%20en-route%20from%20Churachandpur%20to%20Leimakhong%20was%20confronted%20by%20an%20enraged%20mob.%20The%20mob%20forcibly%20took%20away%20four%20of%20them%2C%20while%20one%20escaped.%20One%20person%20from%20the%20group%20was%20later%20rescued%20by%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manipur%20Police%20(%40manipur_police)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanipur_police%2Fstatus%2F1721977018101936457%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fabductions-gunfight-mark-tense-day-in-manipur-9017843%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20alleged%20that%20the%20Meitei%20radical%20group%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20was%20behind%20the%20abduction.%20The%20Forum%20urged%20central%20security%20forces%20to%20launch%20search%20operations%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20fear%20they%20may%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20being%20tortured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20in%20the%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%20village%20when%20five%20civilians%20in%20a%20Bolero%20car%20were%20stopped%20at%20a%20security%20checkpost.%20Soon%20a%20mob%20appeared%20and%20abducted%20the%20four%2C%20including%20two%20women.%20The%20central%20security%20forces%20deployed%20there%20could%20only%20rescue%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmother-3-family-members-of-soldier-abducted-by-mob-in-manipur-father-injured%2Farticle67509763.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20source%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Forum%2C%20Haokip%20was%20rescued%20by%20security%20personnel%20after%20attackers%20left%20him