%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20may%20in%20turn%20trigger%20an%20Iranian%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F9051b052-0b11-4c07-9a0e-264ae73b03a7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%3EHezbollah%20chief%20Hassan%20Nasrullah%20seemed%20to%20anticipate%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20explicitly%20warned%20the%20US%20of%20consequences%20that%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20different%20from%20the%20catastrophic%20American%20involvement%20in%20Lebanon%E2%80%99s%20civil%20war%20in%20the%20early%201980s.%20Ironically%2C%20this%20is%20also%20the%2040th%20anniversary%20year%20of%20the%20suicide%20bombing%20of%20the%20barracks%20housing%20US%20forces%20in%20Beirut%20International%20Airport%20in%20October%201983%20in%20which%20220%20Marines%2C%2018%20sailors%20and%20three%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20forcing%20a%20US%20withdrawal%20from%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20locus%20of%20US%20strategy%20in%20West%20Asia%20may%20be%20shifting%20from%20diplomacy%2C%20which%20has%20anyway%20lost%20traction.%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20attempts%20to%20address%20mounting%20international%20criticism%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20horrific%20war%20crimes%20by%20diverting%20attention%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pause%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20unceremoniously%20shot%20down%20by%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20pounding%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20moved%20in%20on%20Friday.%20It%20has%20reportedly%20advanced%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Gaza%20City%20but%20not%20entered%20the%20Hamas%20stronghold.%20Fierce%20urban%20fighting%20is%20expected%20when%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEqually%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%E2%80%99s%20hurried%20attempt%20to%20promote%20a%20vague%20outline%20for%20a%20postwar%20Gaza%20that%20might%20include%20a%20combination%20of%20a%20revitalised%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20a%20peacekeeping%20force%2C%20etc%2C%20has%20been%20met%20with%20a%20distinct%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20at%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20on%20the%20weekend%20in%20Amman%20with%20Arab%20foreign%20ministers%20%E2%80%95%20from%20Jordan%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20the%20UAE%20%E2%80%95%20who%20instead%20demanded%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20while%20Blinken%20said%20Washington%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20push%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20travelled%20to%20Ramallah%20from%20Amman%2C%20where%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20also%20gave%20him%20short%20shrift%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20would%20only%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20the%20framework%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20political%20solution%E2%80%9D%20including%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20furthermore%2C%20that%20security%20and%20peace%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20by%20ending%20the%20occupation%20of%20territories%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CState%20of%20Palestine%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20by%20recognising%20East%20Jerusalem%20as%20its%20capital.%20The%20meeting%20lasted%20for%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20and%20ended%20without%20public%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China%20and%20the%20UAE%20have%20called%20for%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F148dfe05-a994-401b-8800-500f9b31f40d%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F148dfe05-a994-401b-8800-500f9b31f40d%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1699496422598000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2KdicsagZ14jBLE193W20w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0closed-door%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20in%20another%20attempt%20to%20seek%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2