EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20usually%20critically%20ill%20patients%20had%20to%20go%20to%20cities%20for%20treatment%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%20or%20support%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20would%20die%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Those%20who%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20city%20would%20visit%20faith%20healers%20and%20waste%20the%20golden%20hour%20for%20the%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20that%20medical%20officers%20at%20the%20primary%20health%20centres%20would%20be%20reluctant%20to%20treat%20such%20cases%20as%20they%20either%20lacked%20antivenoms%20or%20necessary%20equipment%20such%20as%20ventilator%20support.%20They%20lack%20training%20to%20handle%20such%20emergency%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20started%20equipping%20his%20hospital%20with%20life%20saving%20equipment%20like%20cardiac%20monitors%2C%20ventilators%2C%20and%20oxygen%20cylinders%2C%20so%20that%20he%20could%20save%20lives%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20Over%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20his%20efforts%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20mission%20that%20aims%20at%20achieving%20zero%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F78205%2Findiansnakes-jose-louies-snakebites-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnakebite%20deaths%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Dos%20%26amp%3B%20Don%E2%80%99ts%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%20Monsoons%20are%20hectic%20when%20at%20least%2012%20patients%20are%20rushed%20to%20the%20medical%20facility%20in%20a%20day.%20Without%20any%20trained%20medical%20staff%20support%2C%20the%20couple%20works%20round%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3