of%20snakebite.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20snake%20bite%2C%20the%20person%20starts%20panicking.%20It%20can%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20high%20blood%20pressure.%20The%20family%20should%20assure%20the%20person%20that%20they%20do%20not%20need%20to%20worry%20as%20timely%20treatment%20will%20save%20their%20lives.%20Also%2C%20a%20person%20should%20not%20walk%20or%20run%20as%20blood%20will%20circulate%20to%20the%20heart%20and%20brain.%20The%20patient%20should%20be%20transferred%20safely%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20a%20lateral%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20informs%20that%20with%20intensive%20care%20management%20and%20administering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F158165%2Fiit-delhi-kerala-floods-snakes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantivenom%20doses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lives%20can%20be%20saved.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20been%20providing%20free%20treatment%20at%20sub-divisional%20government%20hospital%20Manchar%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years%20and%20regularly%20training%20medical%20officers%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%20mission%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%20Recently%2C%20they%20organised%20awareness%20programmes%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20Satara%2C%20and%20Pune%20districts%20and%20claim%20to%20have%20trained%2010%2C000%20students%20and%202%2C000%20teachers%20in%20tribal%20schools%20to%20help%20them%20identify%20venomous%20and%20nonvenomous%20snakes%2C%20and%20the%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20in%20snakebite%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319.