to%20do%20thanks%20to%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20use%20a%20lithium%20ion%20battery%2C%20which%20has%20a%20backup%20of%20four%20hours.%20Now%2C%20I%20had%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time%2C%20without%20increasing%20the%20size%20of%20the%20cell.%20I%20applied%20the%20concept%20of%20control%20systems%20to%20increase%20the%20backup%20time.%20I%20did%20various%20trials%20using%20the%20pulse%20width%20modulation%20algorithm%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20result.%20This%20algorithm%20helped%20me%20optimise%20energy%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20algorithm%20further%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20developed%20a%20way%20to%20adjust%20the%20bulb%E2%80%99s%20brightness%2C%20which%20extends%20the%20time%20of%20backup.%20If%20you%20lower%20the%20brightness%2C%20you%20get%20a%20longer%20backup.%20The%20bulb%20comes%20with%20settings%20to%20change%20the%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20bulb%20works%2C%20Uday%20states%20that%20the%20technology%20used%20is%20very%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20bulb%20is%20connected%20to%20a%20power%20source%2C%20energy%20gets%20stored%20in%20the%20battery.%20When%20the%20power%20supply%20is%20cut%20off%2C%20the%20bulb%20uses%20the%20energy%20stored%20in%20the%20battery%20to%20glow.%20I%20have%20done%20this%20using%20a%20rectifier%2C%20to%20make%20it%20glow%20during%20a%20power%20outage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIlluminating%20over%207%2C000%20households%20in%205%20states%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20has%20sold%20over%207000%20bulbs%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday3-2-1699023290-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333624%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUday%20has%20sold%20over%207%2C000%20bulbs%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20selling%20this%20through%20his%20venture%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Uday%20Electric%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Rs%20250%20a%20piece%20from%20May%202022.%20The%20bulbs%20come%20with%20a%201%20year%20warranty.%20The%20tagline%20of%20the%20company%20is%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBijli%20gul%20phir%20bhi%20ujjala%20full%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Even%20with%20the%20power%20cut%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20light).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20bootstrapped%20the%20venture%20with%20Rs%2030%2C000%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20buy%20the%20table%20and%20supplies%20needed%20for%2050%20bulbs.%20For%20the%20sales%2C%20he%20initially%20started%20visiting%20a%20few%20markets%20and%20doing%20the%20sales%20himself.%20Since%20that%20was%20not%20feasible%20in%20all%20areas%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20local%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20to%20sell%20his%20bulb.%20This%20also%20provides%20them%20with%20an%20extra%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20so%20far%20sold%20over%207%2C000%20units%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh