l%20jobs%20to%20starting%20own%20food%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20Class%2010%20in%202001%2C%20he%20started%20working%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer%20for%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20at%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20border%2C%20which%20earned%20him%20Rs%201%2C200%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiscontented%20with%20the%20job%2C%20he%20quit%20in%20a%20year%20and%20moved%20to%20Meghalaya%20to%20work%20in%20a%20coal%20mine.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20coal%20mines%20was%20really%20very%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20blasting%20operations%20often%20induce%20ground%20vibration%20inside%20the%20mine.%20Strong%20vibrations%20damage%20the%20structure%20and%20result%20in%20ceiling%20collapse.%20We%20frequently%20witnessed%20mishaps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20it%20was%20the%20day%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaghi%20Purnima%20%3C%2Fem%3E(auspicious%20full%20moon%20day)%20when%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20village%20was%20inside%20the%20coal%20mine.%20Due%20to%20the%20strong%20vibrations%2C%20a%20ceiling%20collapsed%20and%20he%20got%20trapped%20inside.%20We%20later%20found%20him%20dead%3B%20his%20body%20was%20crushed%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Diganta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDiganta%20Das%2C%20a%20manual%20labour%20of%20Pkg%20food%20industry%20of%20South%20India%2C%20returned%20home%20during%20Covid%20%26amp%3B%20dared%20to%20open%20small%20packaged%20Parota%20making%20units%20in%20Biswanath%20Chariali%20%26amp%3B%20Lakhimpur%2C%20churning%20out%20avg%201200%20packets%20daily%20at%20each%20centre%20capturing%20market%20from%20Tezpur%20to%20Tinsukia.%201%2F3%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmBzcV5sdEV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmBzcV5sdEV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mrinal%20Talukdar%20(%40mrinaltalukdar8)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmrinaltalukdar8%2Fstatus%2F1640331493384790016%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20devastated%20and%20he%20decided%20to%20pack%20his%20bag%20and%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20left%20for%20Sikkim%20where%20he%20started%20working%20again%20as%20a%20construction%20worker.%20After%20two%20more%20years%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Bengaluru.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20youth%20from%20our%20state%20go%20to%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Pune%20for%20work.%20I%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20see%20Bengaluru%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20secured%20the%20work%20of%20a%20security%20guard%20in%20the%20city%20for%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%204%2C500%2C%20but%20amid%20low%20salary%20and%20untimely%20payments%2C%20he%20eventually%20quit%20that%20work%20too.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20problem%20in%20working%20hard%2C%20but%20I%20wished%20to%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20for%20all%20the%20hard%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20Diganta%20worked%20as%20a%20cook%20in%20Guwahati%20until%20he%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20a%20mixing%20man%20in%20a%20food%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20Mangaluru.%20The%20exposure%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20the%20food%20production%20industry.%20And%20soon%2C%20he%20was%20offered%20the%20job%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20he%20thought%20things%20were%20improving%2C%20he%20met%20with%20an%20accident.%20In%202017%2C%20he%20was%20left%20paralysed%20after%20a%20high-voltage%20electric%20cable%20fell%20on%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20return%20to%20my%20village.%20That%20was%20the%20toughest%20phase%20of%20my%20life%20as%20I%20was%20without%20work%20for%20so%20many%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Diganta%20adding%20that%20it%20took%20almost%20two%20years%20for%20him%20to%20completely%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20parathas%20are%20characterised%20by%20their%20crispy%2C%20flaky%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20texture.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fparota-2-1699019138-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20parathas%20are%20characterised%20by%20their%20crispy%2C%20flaky%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20texture.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20who%20had%20also%20ventured%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E-making%20business%2C%20approached%20Diganta%2C%20given%20his%20experience%20in%20the%20field.%20He%20asked%20for%20help%20in%20establishing%20a%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20Assam.%20Finally%2C%20Diganta%20had%20his%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20Kerala%20delight%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Diganta%20started%20a%20packaged%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20business%20DFF%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333067%2Fdiganta-das-parotta-business-security-guard-daily-fresh-food-video%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOnce%2520a%2520security%2520guard%252C%252032%2Cto%252Deat%2520parottas%2520every%2520day.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Fresh%20Food%3C%2Fa%3E)%20in%20Assam.%20While%20his%20friend%20helped%20him%20with%20the%20machinery%2C%20Diganta%20exhausted%20his%20entire%20life%20savings%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20to%20establish%20the%20business.%20Within%20a%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparathas%20%3C%2Fem%3Egained%20immense%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20their%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20delicacy%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20%E2%80%94%20apart%20is%20their%20ability%20to%20provide%20an%20authentic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330503%2Fmargaret-pak-vinod-kalathil-thattu-restaurant-chicago-kerala-cuisine-onam-sadhya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMalabar%20culinary%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20characterised%20by%20their%20crispy%2C%20flaky%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20texture.%20Their%20ready-to-eat%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20save%20people%20from%20the%20effort%20of%20dough%20kneading%20and%20rolling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyXaBnMIgHI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyXaBnMIgHI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyXaBnMIgHI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EBut%20introducing%20this%20South%20Indian%20culinary%20delight%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20door%20to%20door%20of%20various%20restaurants%20with%20samples%20and%20requested%20people%20to%20try%20our%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20would%20be%20reluctant.%20But%20then%20I%20would%20make%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%20and%20serve%20it%20to%20them%20with%20curry.%20Whoever%20tasted%20it%20appreciated%20the%20quality%20and%20the%20taste%20of%20my%20%3Cem%3Eparathas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Soon%2C%20many%20more%20people%20started%20adding%20this%20dish%20to%20their%20menus%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%2060%20and%20Rs%20100%2C%20these%20packaged%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20come%20in%20packs%20of%20five%20or%2010%20pieces.%20They%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20days%2C%20which%20extends%20up%20to%20seven%20days%20if%20stored%20in%20refrigerators.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20working%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssam-based%20Akhilesh%20Gupta%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20tea%20stall%2C%20loves%20these%20parathas.%20He%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20this%20was%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20absolutely%20loved%20it.%20It%20has%20so%20many%20layers%20and%20is%20so%20soft%20to%20eat.%20We%20keep%20a%20stock%20of%20it%2C%20and%20whenever%20we%20run%20out%20of%20wheat%20at%20home%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20come%20to%20our%20rescue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Diganta%2C%20this%20experience%20helped%20him%20battle%20poverty%20and%20build%20the%20life%20he%20desired%20for%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20qualified%20enough%20to%20get%20a%20high-salaried%20job.%20I%20was%20always%20reluctant%20to%20do%20farming%2C%20so%20I%20always%20ran%20from%20city%20to%20city%20doing%20menial%20jobs.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20climb%20the%20ladder%20of%20success%20right%20from%20the%20place%20where%20it%20all%20started%20%E2%80%94%20my%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Diganta%20Das)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijrte.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fpapers%2Fv9i1%2FA2777059120.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFactors%20and%20Impact%20of%20Rural%20Out-Migration%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Published%20by%20Blue%20Eyes%20Intelligence%20Engineering%20%26amp%3B%20Sciences%20Publication%20in%202020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699021876000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20security%20guard%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Assam's%20Diganta%20Das%20returned%20to%20his%20village%20and%20launched%20his%20own%20startup%20to%20sell%20the%20popular%20Malabar%20parottas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Swimmer%20Escaped%20the%20British%20in%20the%20Ganga%2C%20Suffered%20Bullet%20Wound%20%26amp%3B%20Won%20Gold%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Indians%20joined%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263172%2Fmahatma-gandhi-jayanti-best-quotes-inspiring-heroes-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMohandas%20Karamchand%20(Mahatma)%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20mass%20civil%20disobedience%20against%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%201930.%20Popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F155445%2Fkhurshed-framji-nariman-mumbai-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECivil%20Disobedience%20Movement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20marked%20by%20protest%20rallies%20across%20a%20plethora%20of%20villages%2C%20towns%20and%20cities.%20Among%20the%20millions%20who%20participated%20in%20this%20landmark%20movement%20was%20a%2010-year-old%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAttending%20a%20public%20rally%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Ganga%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20a%20holy%20city%20in%20present-day%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20this%20young%20boy%20got%20caught%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20police%20crackdown.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20began%20lathi-charging%20protestors%2C%20this%2010-year-old%20boy%20%E2%80%9Cjumped%20into%20the%20River%20Ganges%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20police%20in%20between%20the%20boats%E2%80%9D%20and%20hid%20underwater.%20Meanwhile%2C%20as%20a%202014%20media%20report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%2010%20km%20swimming%20competition%20was%20going%20on%20over%20the%20Ganges.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20hide%20himself%2C%20he%20also%20joined%20the%20competition%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20goes%20on%20to%20add.%20To%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20bewilderment%2C%20he%20finished%20third%20in%20this%20race.%20It%20was%20the%20start%20of%20something%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20boy%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20Sachin%20Nag%2C%20a%20legendary%20swimming%20champion%20and%20gold%20medal%20winner%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20100%20m%20freestyle%20event%20at%20the%201951%20Asian%20Games%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Till%20today%2C%20it%20remains%20India%E2%80%99s%20only%20gold%20medal%20in%20swimming%20events%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331761%2Fram-baboo-daily-wager-uttar-pradesh-wins-bronze-medal-in-asian-games-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAsian%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20love%20of%20swimming%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20Bengali%20family%20in%20Varanasi%20in%201920%2C%20Nag%20found%20his%20love%20for%20swimming%20on%20the%20Ganga.%20From%20the%20moment%20he%20surprised%20everyone%20in%20that%20accidental%20race%20in%201930%2C%20he%20competed%20in%20many%20local%20swimming%20competitions%20till%201936%20and%20often%20finished%20in%20the%20first%20two%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20year%2C%20Jamini%20Das%2C%20a%20well-known%20swimmer%2C%20coach%20and%20captain%20of%20the%20Indian%20water%20polo%20team%20in%20the%201948%20London%20Olympics%2C%20made%20his%20way%20to%20Varanasi%20from%20Kolkata%20(Calcutta).%20Representing%20the%20Calcutta-based%20Hatkhola%20Club%2C%20Das%20was%20accompanied%20by%20young%20swimming%20talent%20who%20had%20come%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20competition%20in%20Varanasi.%20At%20this%20competition%2C%20Das%20saw%20a%20young%20and%20untrained%20Nag%20beat%20the%20best%20his%20club%20had%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpon%20witnessing%20this%20talent%2C%20Das%20invited%20Nag%20to%20come%20to%20Calcutta%20and%20train%20with%20him.%20In%20this%20new%20bustling%20city%2C%20the%20young%20Nag%20trained%20with%20the%20club%20and%20stayed%20at%20Das%E2%80%99%20house.%20For%20Nag%2C%20moving%20to%20Calcutta%20was%20the%20break%20he%20needed%20to%20train%20and%20compete%20at%20a%20higher%20level.%20Nag%20began%20training%20and%20competing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Hatkhola%20Club%20in%20the%20Bengal%20state%20championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20he%20beat%20the%20best%20the%20region%20had%20to%20offer%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20100%20m%20and%20400%20m%20freestyle%20events%20in%201938.%20In%20the%20following%20year%2C%20he%20equalled%20the%20national%20record%20for%20the%20100%20m%20freestyle%20event%20with%20a%20time%20of%201%20minute%20and%204%20seconds.%20At%20the%20same%20competition%2C%20he%20broke%20the%20record%20in%20the%20200%20m%20freestyle%20event%20with%20a%20time%20of%202%20minutes%20and%2029%20seconds.%20In%201940%2C%20he%20broke%20the%20100%20m%20freestyle%20record%20set%20by%20fellow%20swimmer%20Dilip%20Mitra%20with%20a%20time%20of%201%20minute%20and%204%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20biography%2C%20this%20record%20stood%20for%2031%20years.%20He%20would%20go%20on%20to%20win%20the%20state%20100%20m%20freestyle%20title%20continuously%20for%20nine%20years.%20By%20the%20mid-1940s%2C%20however%2C%20Nag%20began%20harbouring%20dreams%20of%20competing%20on%20a%20world%20stage%2C%20particularly%20the%20London%20Olympics%20of%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETragedy%20followed%20by%20resilience%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20a%20year%20before%20in%20January%201947%2C%20Nag%20suffered%20a%20serious%20injury%20which%20could%20have%20jeopardised%20his%20chances%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Olympic%20Games.%20This%20was%20a%20time%20of%20great%20violence%20and%20chaos.%20Only%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20earlier%2C%20Calcutta%20had%20witnessed%20bloody%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F218600%2Fdelhi-communal-riots-mumbai-bhiwandi-ips-officer-suresh-khopade-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20riots%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20much%20evidence%20of%20how%20the%20accident%20actually%20took%20place%2C%20what%20remains%20uncontested%20is%20that%20Nag%20was%20returning%20from%20a%20training%20session%20when%20a%20bullet%20struck%20him%20on%20his%20right%20leg%2C%20shattering%20his%20femur.%20Severely%20injured%2C%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20for%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20was%20discharged%2C%20the%20doctor%20told%20him%20that%20it%20would%20take%20at%20least%20two%20years%20before%20he%20could%20get%20back%20to%20swimming.%20It%20was%20evident%20that%20Nag%E2%80%99s%20chance%20at%20competing%20in%20the%20Olympics%20was%20under%20severe%20jeopardy.%20Determined%20to%20compete%2C%20he%20resumed%20training%20just%20six%20months%20after%20the%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20his%20recovery%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20family%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20rejoined%20a%20local%20swimming%20club%20while%20getting%20treatment%20from%20local%20masseurs.%20But%20recovering%20from%20a%20serious%20injury%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20hurdle%20he%20had%20to%20overcome.%20Back%20in%20the%20late%201940s%2C%20athletes%20representing%20India%20had%20to%20bear%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20the%20expenses%20required%20to%20compete%20in%20such%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20pay%20for%20his%20trip%20to%20London%2C%20he%20took%20up%20work%20washing%20vehicles%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20before%20training.%20Despite%20taking%20up%20all%20sorts%20of%20work%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20gather%20the%20requisite%20funds.%20Nag%20was%20about%20to%20give%20up%20on%20his%20dream%20when%20Hemanta%20Mukhopadhyay%2C%20a%20singer%2C%20heard%20about%20his%20plight%20and%20decided%20to%20raise%20funds.%20One%20of%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20singer%20raised%20funds%20was%20through%20a%20musical%20performance%20at%20the%20Uttara%20Cinema%20Hall%20in%20North%20Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENag%20finally%20had%20the%20money%20to%20realise%20his%20dream%20of%20competing%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20He%20finished%20in%20sixth%20place%20at%20the%201948%20London%20Olympics%20in%20the%20100%20m%20freestyle%20event.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20he%20also%20played%20for%20the%20Indian%20water%20polo%20team%20and%20scored%20four%20goals%20in%20a%207%E2%80%934%20win%20versus%20Chile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20939px)%20100vw%2C%20939px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22939%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swimmer%20Sachin%20Nag%20from%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-scaled.jpg%20939w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-110x300.jpg%20110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-376x1024.jpg%20376w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-768x2093.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSachin-Nag-2-1699019182-150x409.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333580%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESachin%20Nag%2C%20the%20legendary%20swimmer.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMoment%20of%20Glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENag%E2%80%99s%20moment%20of%20glory%2C%20however%2C%20came%20three%20years%20later%20at%20the%20inaugural%20edition%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20In%20a%20dazzling%20display%20on%208%20March%2C%201951%2C%20he%20secured%20gold%20in%20the%20100%20m%20freestyle%20event%20with%20a%20time%20of%201%20minute%20and%204.7%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWatching%20Nag%20perform%20his%20magic%20in%20the%20audience%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20According%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20Nehru%20was%20so%20overjoyed%20that%20he%20broke%20protocol%2C%20embraced%20Nag%2C%20and%20presented%20him%20with%20the%20red%20rose%20from%20the%20breast%20pocket%20of%20his%20coat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20press%20reports%2C%20Nag%20noted%20how%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20moments%20in%20his%20life.%20Besides%20winning%20gold%20in%20the%20100%20m%20freestyle%2C%20he%20also%20picked%20bronze%20medals%20in%20the%204%C3%97100%20m%20freestyle%20relay%20and%20the%203%C3%97100%20m%20freestyle%20relay.%20He%20would%20also%20go%20on%20to%20compete%20in%20the%201952%20Helsinki%20Olympics%2C%20representing%20India%20in%20water%20polo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20incredible%20achievements%20in%20the%20pool%2C%20he%20would%20train%20future%20generations%20of%20Indian%20swimmers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F88621%2Farati-saha-first-indian-asian-woman-swim-english-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArati%20Saha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20Asian%20woman%20to%20cross%20the%20English%20channel%20in%201959%2C%20and%20Nafisa%20Ali%2C%20a%20national%20champion%20in%20the%20early%201970s%20who%20was%20also%20crowned%20Miss%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDesire%20for%20recognition%2C%20acknowledgement%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20many%20achievements%20for%20the%20country%20against%20incredible%20odds%2C%20Nag%20passed%20away%20on%2019%20August%2C%201987%2C%20without%20real%20recognition%20or%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202014%2C%20Ashoke%20Kumar%20Nag%2C%20his%20son%20and%20a%20Kolkata-based%20insurance%20agent%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe