onally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20humble%20background%20to%20his%20work%20getting%20recognised%20on%20global%20platforms%2C%20his%20story%20is%20an%20inspiring%20one.%20And%20he%20is%20rightly%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98Father%20of%20Indian%20Photojournalism%E2%80%99.%20We%20take%20a%20look%20at%20his%20incredible%20journey%20and%20the%20moments%20that%20shaped%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20fated%20photographer%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20graduation%20in%20Arts%20from%20Maharaja%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Mysuru%2C%20Satyan%20joined%20as%20an%20engine%20inspector%20at%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics.%20He%20then%20worked%20as%20a%20teacher%20at%20a%20school%20followed%20by%20working%20as%20a%20newsreader%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Akashvani%E2%80%99%20radio%20station.%20All%20this%20time%2C%20he%20remained%20connected%20with%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20love%20of%20photography%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%201948%2C%20when%20a%20vacancy%20opened%20up%20for%20a%20staff%20photographer%20at%20the%20newly%20launched%20Deccan%20Herald%20%E2%80%94%20an%20English%20daily%20based%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20Satyan%20grabbed%20the%20opportunity.%20This%20was%20his%20first%20professional%20stint%20with%20a%20camera%20and%20he%20delivered%20to%20impress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201445px)%20100vw%2C%201445px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T%20S%20Satyan%20was%20known%20for%20his%20trademark%20black%20and%20white%20pictures%20that%20captured%20the%20mood%20of%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%