bassador%20Nathaniel%20Fick%2C%20former%20PM%20of%20Australia%20Kevin%20Rudd%20and%20comedian%20Trevor%20Noah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Nageswaran%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20my%20friends%20from%20iSPIRT%20arranged%20for%20me%20to%20join%20Arun%20Pai%E2%80%99s%20Bengaluru%20walk%20on%2024%20July.%20He%20was%20simply%20brilliant%20with%20his%20erudition%2C%20wit%2C%20and%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20city.%20His%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20Bangalorean%20came%20through%20so%20well%20that%20I%20was%20infected%20with%20that%20pride.%20He%20made%20Sir%20M%20Visweswaraiya%20and%20the%20Mysore%20Maharaja%20come%20alive%20with%20his%20vivid%20descriptions%20of%20their%20vision%20and%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20a%20perfect%20start%20to%20the%20day%20and%20made%20my%20short%20visit%20to%20Bengaluru%20entirely%20memorable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20adulation%2C%20one%20experience%20outshines%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%20Karnataka%20played%20host%20to%20over%2010%20important%20summit%20meetings%20over%20the%20year%20including%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20And%20Pai%20was%20the%20official%20representative%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Karnataka%20for%20designing%20and%20planning%20the%20city%20tours%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127339%2Fcalcutta-houses-instagram-photo-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcursions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20last%20detail%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sites%20around%20cities%20like%20Mysuru%2C%20Hampi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20experience%20at%20Hampi%2C%20Pai%20says%20it%20was%20phenomenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20three%20days%2C%20I%20highlighted%20globa